Here's my number one rule:

175
00:08:33,377 --> 00:08:35,044
要是你逼我睡车上
If you're going to make me sleep in it,

176
00:08:35,046 --> 00:08:37,513
我就得在车上喝东西
I am going to drink in it.

177
00:08:37,515 --> 00:08:38,881
那就小心点
Well, just be careful.

178
00:08:38,883 --> 00:08:40,382
我只剩一条消毒湿巾了
I only have one Clorox wipe

179
00:08:40,384 --> 00:08:42,551
它得用到我下次生日为止
that has to last till my next birthday,

180
00:08:42,553 --> 00:08:44,887
况且它都不大湿润了
and it's already lost a lot of its moisture.

181
00:08:46,807 --> 00:08:50,059
我不明白为什么要空坐在这
I don't see why we have to just sit here.

182
00:08:50,061 --> 00:08:51,227
我们不能开这车
We can't drive it.

183
00:08:51,229 --> 00:08:53,028
我爸说了万一出事
My dad said if anything happens to it,

184
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:54,230
我们要负责的
we'll be responsible.

185
00:08:54,232 --> 00:08:55,681
哪会发生什么事
What could possibly happen

186
00:08:55,683 --> 00:08:59,368
咱可是抽着大麻直通墨西哥
on a weed run to deep Tijuana?

187
00:08:59,370 --> 00:09:01,070
其实我倒希望自己从没有过这车
You know, I wish this car never came,

188
00:09:01,072 --> 00:09:02,788
从未坐上它
and I wish I never sat in it.

189
00:09:02,790 --> 00:09:04,540
这就跟我不去巴尼精品店一个道理
It's the same reason I don't go to Barneys.

190
00:09:04,542 --> 00:09:07,159
买不起的东西还是离远点好
I don't like to be around things I can't afford anymore.

191
00:09:07,161 --> 00:09:10,379
也跟我不去一元店是同一个道理
Same reason I don't go to the 99 Cent Store.

192
00:09:10,381 --> 00:09:11,880
那边有套Nerf网球
There's a Nerf tennis set

193
00:09:11,882 --> 00:09:14,133
球拍在地上 球在垃圾桶里
half on the floor, half in the bin,

194
00:09:14,135 --> 00:09:17,219
都没被我带回家
none of it going home with me.

195
00:09:17,221 --> 00:09:19,972
我本想以积极的心态度过今年的生日
I was trying to be positive about my birthday this year,

196
00:09:19,974 --> 00:09:22,591
要不是我爸东窗事发
but, Max, if things hadn't happened with my father,

197
00:09:22,593 --> 00:09:24,810
今晚就会是我的魔幻般的庆生夜
tonight would have been a magical birthday for me.

198
00:09:24,812 --> 00:09:26,562
还是有点魔术的
Hey, there was some magic.

199
00:09:26,564 --> 00:09:30,482
我就亲自变没了五杯加伏特酒的雪碧
I personally made five vodka Sprites disappear.

200
00:09:30,484 --> 00:09:32,651
厉害吧
Ta-da!

201
00:09:32,653 --> 00:09:35,321
我或许已经驾着车 开去汉普顿斯
I would've got in the car and driven out to the Hamptons,

202
00:09:35,323 --> 00:09:37,106
还能坐上整晚的沙滩
and we'd sit on the beach all night

203
00:09:37,108 --> 00:09:39,275
吃着一个由当地人抓的龙虾
having lobster caught by one of the townies

204
00:09:39,277 --> 00:09:42,444
边喝香槟 边醉醺醺地自拍
and drink champagne while taking duckface selfies

205
00:09:42,446 --> 00:09:44,163
直到天亮
till the sun came up.

206
00:09:46,834 --> 00:09:49,918
补充一下 我就是你想象中的那个当地人
FYI, I'm the townie in this scenario,

207
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:52,037
憎恶着你们所有人
and I hate all of you.

208
00:09:52,039 --> 00:09:55,274
现在我却过着最糟糕的生日 和我憧憬的完全不同
Instead of doing any of that, I'm having the worst birthday.

209
00:09:55,276 --> 00:09:56,925
也许黛米・摩尔步入花甲之年
I probably feel worse than Demi Moore did

210
00:09:56,927 --> 00:10:00,129
都没我这么难过
when she turned 50.

211
00:10:00,131 --> 00:10:02,681
洗洗睡吧
Yes, just go to sleep.

212
00:10:02,683 --> 00:10:05,017
明天起来就会感觉好多了
You'll feel better tomorrow when you wake up.

213
00:10:05,019 --> 00:10:06,769
要是那个拿着把刀说捅死我们的人
I mean, if that guy with the switchblade

214
00:10:06,771 --> 00:10:08,721
