doesn't come back like he promised he would.

215
00:10:14,845 --> 00:10:16,812
醒醒 Caroline
Caroline.

216
00:10:16,814 --> 00:10:18,030
Caroline 快起来
Caroline, wake up.

217
00:10:21,068 --> 00:10:22,151
我们到沙滩了
We're at the beach.

218
00:10:22,153 --> 00:10:25,788
我载你来到了汉普顿斯
I drove us out to the Hamptons.

219
00:10:25,790 --> 00:10:28,324
生日快乐
Happy birthday!

220
00:10:28,326 --> 00:10:32,828
我们在汉普顿斯?
We're in the Hamptons?

221
00:10:32,830 --> 00:10:36,332
我们竟然在汉普顿斯?
We're in the Hamptons?

222
00:10:36,334 --> 00:10:38,334
我们怎么来汉普顿斯的?
How are we in the Hamptons?

223
00:10:38,336 --> 00:10:40,219
我睡了多久?
How long have I been sleeping?

224
00:10:40,221 --> 00:10:42,004
三四个小时吧
Three hours, give or take.

225
00:10:42,006 --> 00:10:44,723
你放了两次屁
You farted twice.

226
00:10:44,725 --> 00:10:46,642
我怎么不会醒来?
How did I not wake up?

227
00:10:46,644 --> 00:10:48,594
是吧 确实很糟糕
I know. It was pretty bad.

228
00:10:51,015 --> 00:10:54,650
你放完那个屁后 我还以为我们路过臭蛋乡了
After that last one, I thought we were going through Egg Town.

229
00:10:56,904 --> 00:10:58,437
Max 你又做坏事了
Max, you did it again.

230
00:10:58,439 --> 00:11:00,155
你给我下了安眠药 是吧?
You roofied me, didn't you?

231
00:11:00,157 --> 00:11:02,391
自然是有的
Of course I did.

232
00:11:02,393 --> 00:11:04,827
你在那边哭喊着嚷嚷关于汉普顿斯的美梦
You were crying and babbling about the Hamptons,

233
00:11:04,829 --> 00:11:07,279
我只能把你放倒啊
so I had to put you down.

234
00:11:07,281 --> 00:11:09,415
你答应过我不会再这么做的
You promised you wouldn't again.

235
00:11:09,417 --> 00:11:11,583
上次我整整昏迷了两天
The last time, I was out for two days.

236
00:11:11,585 --> 00:11:14,036
但我真的想把"权力的游戏"看完啊
Yeah, I really just needed to get through Game of Thrones

237
00:11:14,038 --> 00:11:17,289
特别是看乱伦戏时没人吵我
without someone talking during the incest.

238
00:11:19,710 --> 00:11:21,844
你究竟有啥毛病啊?
What is wrong with you?

239
00:11:21,846 --> 00:11:24,847
有纸笔吗?
Have you got a pen and paper?

240
00:11:24,849 --> 00:11:26,715
你明明知道我不想这么做
You knew I didn't want to do this.

241
00:11:26,717 --> 00:11:30,185
你什么事都不想做 所以我替你做了
You never want to do anything, so I did it for you.

242
00:11:30,187 --> 00:11:33,639
你开走了一辆价值45万的车
You took a $450,000 car,

243
00:11:33,641 --> 00:11:37,059
一辆碰都不该碰的车
a car we're not even supposed to be touching,

244
00:11:37,061 --> 00:11:39,395
还开来汉普顿斯兜风
on a joyride to the Hamptons?

245
00:11:39,397 --> 00:11:42,865
是你想来这的
You wanted to be here.

246
00:11:42,867 --> 00:11:43,899
现在来了
You are here.

247
00:11:43,901 --> 00:11:45,150
就尽管享受吧
Just enjoy it.

248
00:11:45,152 --> 00:11:48,036
我没心情享受
I can't enjoy it.

249
00:11:49,457 --> 00:11:50,856
Scotty 到桥上来
Scotty to the bridge.

250
00:11:50,858 --> 00:11:52,124
我是科克船长
This is Captain Kirk.

251
00:11:52,126 --> 00:11:53,659
斯科迪到桥上来
Scotty to the bridge.

252
00:11:56,747 --> 00:12:00,916
你把车开过沙丘 来这沙滩的?
You drove over the dunes and onto the beach?

253
00:12:00,918 --> 00:12:03,051
不是故意的
Not intentionally.

254
00:12:03,053 --> 00:12:05,087
我试过刹车 但这车像在对我说
I tried to stop it, but this car was like,

255
00:12:05,089 --> 00:12:06,839
冲啊 姑娘
"Mm, no, girl."

256
00:12:09,427 --> 00:12:10,893
天啊
Oh, my God.

257
00:12:10,895 --> 00:12:13,262
车上有划痕吗?
Did it get any scratches?

258
00:12:13,264 --> 00:12:16,982
Max 从车里出来 帮我找找有没划痕
Max, get out of the car, and help me look for scratches.

259
00:12:16,984 --> 00:12:21,403
你说过你来汉普顿斯会开心起来的
You said you were more fun in the Hamptons.

260
00:12:21,405 --> 00:12:23,572
才不是这回事
Not true.

261
00:12:24,492 --> 00:12:28,610
苏禄先生 开炮 
Mr. Sulu, fire all phasers.

262
00:12:28,612 --> 00:12:31,580
没划痕 兰博基尼没事
No scratches. The Lamborghini is fine.

263
00:12:31,582 --> 00:12:34,700
多亏了你 我也做了一回租车族
But thanks to you, I'm a Rent-A-Wreck.

264
00:12:37,455 --> 00:12:39,838
行了 该把车开回去了
Come on, we have to get this car back.

265
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:41,590
会的 真是的 放松点
We will. Jeez, relax.

266
00:12:41,592 --> 00:12:42,791
还有时间呢
We still have time.

267
00:12:42,793 --> 00:12:45,210
听着 你说你想来这
Look, you said you wanted to be here.

268
00:12:45,212 --> 00:12:46,845
现在到了 我们别马上走
You're here, and we are not leaving

269
00:12:46,847 --> 00:12:48,180
你得先享受下这沙滩
till you do something beach-y,

270
00:12:48,182 --> 00:12:50,182
比如踏踏浪
like walk in the water

271
00:12:50,184 --> 00:12:54,720
或者找一下被鲨鱼咬断的残骸
or find a half-eaten lady from Jaws.

272
00:12:54,722 --> 00:12:57,022
没 没门 现在就走
No. No way. Let's go.

273
00:12:57,024 --> 00:12:58,273
就试着脱下鞋子嘛
Just take off your shoes or something.

274
00:12:58,275 --> 00:12:59,691
不要
No.

275
00:12:59,693 --> 00:13:01,360
脱下鞋子 感受下沙滩
Just take off your shoes and feel the sand.

276
00:13:01,362 --> 00:13:02,611
Max! 住手 Max
Max! Max, stop.

277
00:13:02,613 --> 00:13:04,313
我已经好久没有修过脚了
I haven't had a proper pedicure

278
00:13:04,315 --> 00:13:06,615
上一次是在贾斯汀・汀布莱克发单曲之时
since Justin Timberlake released a single.

279
00:13:06,617 --> 00:13:09,284
好了 现在可以动动你的脚了
There. Now move your foot around.

280
00:13:09,286 --> 00:13:10,619
不要
No.

281
00:13:10,621 --> 00:13:12,538
不 不 不
No. No! No.

282
00:13:12,540 --> 00:13:13,989
啊
Oh. Oh, yeah.

283
00:13:13,991 --> 00:13:16,625
感觉好爽
That feels nice.

284
00:13:16,627 --> 00:13:18,627
冰凉的细沙在趾间滑过
The cold sand between my toes.

285
00:13:18,629 --> 00:13:20,045
Max 别看我的脚
But, Max, don't look.

286
00:13:20,047 --> 00:13:21,997
中间的指甲简直惨不忍睹
That middle nail's a horror show.

287
00:13:21,999 --> 00:13:23,298
太晚了
Too late.

288
00:13:23,300 --> 00:13:27,503
有那么一会儿 我还觉得它是颗开心果
I thought it was a pistachio for a second.

289
00:13:27,505 --> 00:13:30,305
Max 你有多喜欢海滩
Max, how much do you love the beach?

290
00:13:30,307 --> 00:13:32,424
我不知道 从来没去过
I don't know. I've never been to one.

291
00:13:32,426 --> 00:13:34,293
你从来没去过海滩?
You've never been to a beach?

292
00:13:34,295 --> 00:13:35,894
那又怎么了?
No. What's the point?

293
00:13:35,896 --> 00:13:37,679
我还没有金属探测仪呢
I don't own a metal detector.

294
00:13:40,968 --> 00:13:42,684
好了 时间到
Well, time's up.

295
00:13:42,686 --> 00:13:44,353
可我们才坐下啊
But we just sat down.

296
00:13:44,355 --> 00:13:45,988
我知道 但如果现在走
I know, but if we leave right now,

297
00:13:45,990 --> 00:13:47,990
那我们就还有时间
we'll still have enough time to blow through

298
00:13:47,992 --> 00:13:49,358
掠过麦当劳汽车餐厅
a McDonald's drive-through

299
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:52,544
就像"回到未来"演的那样
like something from Back to the Future.

300
00:13:52,546 --> 00:13:54,530
我要把咱们的名字写在沙子上
Well, I'm gonna write our names in the sand

301
00:13:54,532 --> 00:13:56,081
很感谢你给我下药
'cause it was a really nice thing

302
00:13:56,083 --> 00:13:57,666
把我绑架到这里
for you to drug me, kidnap me,

303
00:13:57,668 --> 00:14:00,536
然后偷我的车带我到这里
and steal my car to get me out here.

304
00:14:00,538 --> 00:14:04,006
朋友嘛
Hey, we're friends.

305
00:14:04,008 --> 00:14:06,174
好了 掉个头先
All right, I'll just turn this baby around.

306
00:14:10,214 --> 00:14:11,280
哦噢
Uh-oh.

307
00:14:13,300 --> 00:14:15,934
哦噢什么呀?
What's "uh-oh"?

308
00:14:15,936 --> 00:14:18,770
哦噢什么呀?
What is "uh-oh"?

309
00:14:18,772 --> 00:14:21,106
卡在沙子里了?
Are we stuck in the sand?

310
00:14:21,108 --> 00:14:26,061
你这个"哦噢"用得非常到位
You have correctly identified the meaning of "uh-oh."

311
00:14:26,063 --> 00:14:27,896
我们连话都不用说
I love that we don't need full sentences

312
00:14:27,898 --> 00:14:30,399
就能心有灵犀了
to communicate anymore.

313
00:14:40,559 --> 00:14:41,775
再试试
Try it again.

314
00:14:44,396 --> 00:14:45,462
不行
Nope.

315
00:14:45,464 --> 00:14:46,311
从运动员家逃出来
I've had less trouble

316
00:14:46,311 --> 00:14:48,798
都没这么难
getting out of athlete's apartments.

317
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:50,700
那你得下去推车了
Well, you're gonna have to get out and push.

318
00:14:50,702 --> 00:14:52,452
为什么是我?
Why do I have to push?

319
00:14:52,454 --> 00:14:55,371
因为是你给我下药 绑架我
Because you're the one who drugged me, kidnapped me,

320
00:14:55,373 --> 00:14:56,573
还偷了我的车
and stole my car.

321
00:14:56,575 --> 00:14:57,574
说得好
Exactly.

322
00:14:57,574 --> 00:15:00,994
我都帮你搞定了大部分工作了
I've already done the lion's share of the work.

323
00:15:00,996 --> 00:15:02,912
再说这车是咱俩的
And it's our car.

324
00:15:02,914 --> 00:15:04,380
好吧 我去
Fine, I'll do it.

325
00:15:07,085 --> 00:15:09,385
开门 乌乎拉中尉(星际旅行中"进取号的"总通讯官)
Door's up, Lieutenant Uhura.

326
00:15:09,387 --> 00:15:13,173
都被困在这了 能不贫嘴吗
It stopped being funny when we got stuck.

327
00:15:13,175 --> 00:15:14,808
别担心
God, don't worry.

328
00:15:14,810 --> 00:15:16,593
我曾经徒手把一个
I got a 600-pound woman

329
00:15:16,595 --> 00:15:18,478
600磅重的女人从餐厅座位里弄出来
out of a booth at the diner with my bare hands.

330
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:19,929
我都毫无惧色
I'm fearless.

331
00:15:19,931 --> 00:15:24,267
和那次一样 把她挂到空挡
Toss her in neutral like I did with that lady.

332
00:15:24,269 --> 00:15:26,569
沙子和高跟鞋 这样不行啊
Sand and heels. Not a good combo.

333
00:15:26,571 --> 00:15:29,272
这样不行啊 不行
Not a good combo. Not a good combo.

334
00:15:29,274 --> 00:15:31,774
没事
Oh, all right.

335
00:15:31,776 --> 00:15:34,077
好了
All right.

336
00:15:34,079 --> 00:15:34,994
油门踩到底
I'm gonna floor it.

337
00:15:36,281 --> 00:15:37,280
等我数到三
On the count of three.

338
00:15:37,282 --> 00:15:39,115
一 二...
One, two...

339
00:15:48,627 --> 00:15:51,594
激动了 有点早
I got excited. I went early.

340
00:15:53,181 --> 00:15:55,181
要是每次听见这句我能有一美元
If I had a dime for every time I heard that,

341
00:15:55,183 --> 00:15:57,133
我都能买下这车了
I could buy this car.

342
00:15:57,135 --> 00:15:58,968
没事 再试一次
All right, let's try again.

343
00:15:58,970 --> 00:16:00,770
一 二...
One, two...

344
00:16:15,287 --> 00:16:17,871
这次绝对是故意的
Okay, that was on purpose.

345
00:16:17,873 --> 00:16:20,790
可能吧
A little bit.

346
00:16:20,792 --> 00:16:22,325
真不敢相信
I can't believe it.

347
00:16:22,327 --> 00:16:23,993
真不敢相信我居然不信
I can't believe that I can't believe it,

348
00:16:23,995 --> 00:16:26,162
可我就是不敢相信
but I really can't believe it.

349
00:16:26,164 --> 00:16:27,881
我们遇到这么大的麻烦
We are in very big trouble,

350
00:16:27,883 --> 00:16:31,134
还被困在汉普顿的最烂的沙滩上
and we're not even in the good Hamptons.

351
00:16:31,136 --> 00:16:33,836
我只是想做点好事
I was trying to do something nice.

352
00:16:33,838 --> 00:16:36,973
第一次 也是最后一次
First time, last time.

353
00:16:36,975 --> 00:16:38,841
你知道你是什么吗?
You know what you are?

354
00:16:38,843 --> 00:16:40,476
你是鲁莽他大爷
You are reckless.

355
00:16:40,478 --> 00:16:42,345
这么长时间
You know, all this time,

356
00:16:42,347 --> 00:16:45,315
我一直以为你是个宝马婊
I thought you were a ride-or-die kind of bitch.

357
00:16:45,317 --> 00:16:51,154
我就是个宝马婊怎样
